description:
What does the Bible mean when it talks about people being lost? What does the Bible mean when it talks about people being lost? here’s a story in the Bible of a son who ungratefully leaves his father and loses his way. His father welcomes him back when he chooses to return to him. In the same way, we have all been lost, but because of what Jesus did for us, we can come back to God.
